    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>A &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere} of negative energy ripples out in a 60-foot-radius &amp;Reference[sphere]{sphere} from a point within range. Each creature in that area must make a &amp;Reference[con]{Constitution} saving throw. A target takes 8d6 &amp;Reference[necrotic]{necrotic} damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one.</p>\n<p><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the damage increases by 2d6 for each slot level above 6th.</p>\n</div>",
